# 💸 PerFin

### Modern Offline Personal Finance App

Jetpack Compose • MVVM • Room • Hilt • Offline First</b>

---

## 🚀 Features

- 💰 Add / Edit / Delete transactions  
- 🔄 Income, Expense & Transfer support  
- 🏦 Multi-account management  
- 📊 Real-time balance & insights  
- 🗂 Categories with icons & colors  
- ⚙️ Settings (Dark Mode, Currency, App Lock)  
- 🔒 Fully Offline (Privacy focused)  

---

## 🧠 Architecture

- Clean MVVM architecture  
- Flow-based reactive UI  
- Offline-first data layer  

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Kotlin  
- Jetpack Compose  
- Room Database  
- Hilt DI  
- Coroutines + Flow  
- Navigation Compose  

---

## 🗄 Database

- TransactionEntity  
- AccountEntity  
- CategoryEntity  
- SettingsEntity  

---

## ⚠️ Technical Decisions & Trade-offs

PerFin is designed as an offline-first application using Room, MVVM, and Flow to ensure privacy, performance, and reliability without relying on network connectivity. This simplifies architecture and improves responsiveness but limits real-time sync and multi-device access. Account-based balance calculation is used instead of derived income-expense formulas to maintain financial accuracy, especially with transfers. Due to time constraints, the current implementation is incomplete; however, future scope includes integrating an AI-based chat system to allow users to record transactions via voice and query summaries conversationally. Additionally, while the app is fully offline, import/export functionality can be introduced for backup and portability without compromising privacy.

---

## 📌 Future Scope

- 🤖 AI-based chat assistant (voice + queries)  
- 📊 Advanced analytics  
- ☁️ Backup & restore  
- 📤 Import / Export data  

